snippet.title: FNF: Vs. Okayu Mod Showcase (FC)
snippet.description:
Face off against Nekomata Okayu, a chill catgirl streamer hailing from Hololive, in her original song "Mogu Mogu Yummy." With little onigiri prisoners and cool sunglasses and a cute pastel aesthetic, this short and simple mod is perfect for all of us weebs i mean simps i mean cultured people i mean fans of Vtubers out there!

A mod I created since I've been obsessed with Nekomata Okayu's song "Mogu Mogu Yummy" recently! Download the mod here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/348186
